ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectCTMA Ranger Remission Order
PrecisCTMA RANGER REMISSION ORDER in order to allow CTMA to be eligible for partial remission of customs duties in the amount of approximately $0.6 million – the difference between the 25% tariff CTMA expected to pay, and the 35% tariff it paid.
